bagaimana ini?

233
00:13:31,320 --> 00:13:33,710
Kita bahas lagi masalah Dai Mubai.

234
00:13:35,200 --> 00:13:36,150
Aku bisa bantu apa?

235
00:13:37,030 --> 00:13:37,840
Kau kembali dulu.

236
00:13:38,320 --> 00:13:39,550
Aku diskusi dengan Master.

237
00:13:40,710 --> 00:13:41,230
Pergilah.

238
00:13:46,470 --> 00:13:47,910
Semua yang kau
katakan benar.

239
00:13:48,110 --> 00:13:49,840
Mengalahkan hati itu
bergantung padanya.

240
00:13:49,840 --> 00:13:53,320
Ada satu cara,
