249
00:14:28,840 --> 00:14:32,200
…membantu Sekte Cahaya Qibao
memutasikan Roh Pelindung.

250
00:14:34,110 --> 00:14:37,440
Intinya satu tujuan,
membunuh Bibi Dong.

251
00:14:38,110 --> 00:14:39,150
Apa kata Paman Ning?

252
00:14:39,400 --> 00:14:40,840
Sepertinya mereka ragu.

253
00:14:41,880 --> 00:14:42,550
Kau juga tahu,…

254
00:14:43,640 --> 00:14:45,570
